what_worked: Applied early_filter, pushdown, dimension_cte_isolate: Created early-filter CTEs for dimension tables (date_dim, customer_address, web_site) and pre-materialized the web_returns join with ws_wh. Converted implicit joins to explicit JOIN syntax for better optimizer control.
why_it_worked: Applying selective filters early reduces intermediate row counts before expensive operations; Pushing predicates closer to table scans reduces data volume in upper operators; Pre-filtering all dimension tables into CTEs avoids repeated full-table scans
